OL,3,CWho will be Guernsey's next Chief
OL,4,CMinister?
OL,6,FWith Lyndon Trott deciding not to
OL,7,Fstand for re-election, Guernsey will
OL,8,Fbe getting a new Chief Minister this
OL,9,Fweek.
OL,11,FThe island's fresh set of deputies
OL,12,Fwill decide who takes the top job,
OL,13,FPresident of the Policy and Resources
OL,14,FCommittee, in a vote on Tuesday.
