OL,3,CWho will be Guernsey's next Chief
OL,4,CMinister?
OL,6,FTo get elected, a candidate has to be
OL,7,Fproposed and seconded. The proposer
OL,8,Fwill make a five-minute speech before
OL,9,Fthe Assembly, then the candidate is
OL,10,Fgiven 15 minutes to argue why they are
OL,11,Fbest placed to lead Guernsey for the
OL,12,Fnext four years.
OL,14,FThree candidates are vying for the top
OL,15,Fjob, find out who they are below:
OL,17,FLindsay De Sausmarez
