OL,3,CWho will be Guernsey's next Chief
OL,4,CMinister?
OL,6,FDeputy De Sausmarez is currently the
OL,7,Ffavourite to win the vote on Tuesday.
OL,8,FIf elected, she will become the
OL,9,Fisland's first female Chief Minister.
OL,11,FShe topped the poll at the General
OL,12,FElection earlier this month and was
OL,13,Fthe only candidate to receive the
OL,14,Fbacking of more than half those who
OL,15,Fvoted.
