OL,3,CWho will be Guernsey's next Chief
OL,4,CMinister?
OL,6,FIn the previous States Assembly, De
OL,7,FSausmarez served as the President of
OL,8,FEnvironment and Infrastructure - a
OL,9,Frole which gave her a leading role in
OL,10,Fdevising policy in key areas such as
OL,11,Fhousing.
OL,13,FA key progressive voice in the
OL,14,Fchamber, she also called out bullying
OL,15,Fand inappropriate behaviour in the
OL,16,Flast term.
OL,18,FMark Helyar
