OL,3,CWho will be Guernsey's next Chief
OL,4,CMinister?
OL,6,FDeputy Helyar made clear in his
OL,7,Fmanifesto that he would stand for the
OL,8,Ftop job, having previously served as
OL,9,FTreasury Lead on the first Policy and
OL,10,FResources Committee in the last
OL,11,FStates' term.
OL,13,FHowever, he resigned from the top
OL,14,Fcommittee in late 2023 before a motion
OL,15,Fof no confidence was called in Policy
OL,16,Fand Resources.
OL,18,FHelyar is a keen GST+ supporter and
OL,19,Ftried to implement the tax in 2023.
