OL,3,CWho will be Guernsey's next Chief
OL,4,CMinister?
OL,6,FHe announced himself as a candidate
OL,7,Fafter the election, suggesting he was
OL,8,Fbest placed to unite the States
OL,9,Ftogether, given the current political
OL,10,Fclimate.
OL,12,FHe was also one of the main architects
OL,13,Fof the GST+ package that was approved
OL,14,Fby the States last year.
OL,16,FAn experienced politician, Le Tocq
OL,17,Fpreviously served as the island's
OL,18,FChief Minister from 2014 to 2016, as
OL,19,Fwell as Deputy Chief Minister.
