OL,3,CWho will be Guernsey's next Chief
OL,4,CMinister?
OL,6,FA fourth candidate, Deputy Charles
OL,7,FParkinson, had also thrown his hat
OL,8,Finto the ring following the election.
OL,9,FHowever, ITV News understands he will
OL,10,Fno longer put himself forward and will
OL,11,Fbe backing De Sausmarez instead.
OL,13,FThe vote for the President of Policy
OL,14,Fand Resources will be the first
OL,15,Fofficial business for the newly
OL,16,Felected deputies.
