OL,3,CWho will be Guernsey's next Chief
OL,4,CMinister?
OL,6,FIt starts a week of jostling for
OL,7,Fposition amongst politicians, with
OL,8,Fother members of the senior committee
OL,9,Fdue to be decided following a vote on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,12,FThen on Friday, deputies will choose
OL,13,Fwho they want to be the Presidents of
OL,14,Fthe other committees, with these
OL,15,Fcommittee members set to be elected
OL,16,Fnext week.
